{"tid":1895134,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「黃色經濟圈」富臨炑八要停一停，抖一抖","createTime":"2020-02-24T11:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T12:38:39.000Z","uid":186,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"166a0321dd3cafb601573639c60b94bb7706c03e","tid":1895134,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dsNr2oX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdsNr2oX.jpg&h=d1f2df7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於2019年8月11日舉行的反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動港島東集會，由於北角富臨皇宮酒家聚集福建幫人士，門外更發生打鬥黑衣人和記者事件，引發網民呼籲罷食富臨集團旗下餐廳，其facebook專頁亦有不少批評聲音。<br />\n<br />\n於2020年2月8日，富臨集團旗下灣仔菲林明道的陶源酒家點心師傅2月8日發病確診新型肺炎。富臨集團其後宣佈旗下約20間餐廳短暫休業，並要求員工放無薪假期。"},{"pid":"4429239cd1ced6fb47e963296c95dad03741ad15","tid":1895134,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XS9eM2N.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXS9eM2N.gif&h=63e939f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c64e5ff17877d434dea84ec40093f3e58d8d8ff","tid":1895134,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"食肆廚房停用幾個月乜春蛇蟲鼠蟻都出晒黎 重開返都搵鬼食啦 不如全線執柒咗佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cf47d3851cd7d17f1d2580388734320e49bc29","tid":1895134,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"本身都無人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1016fb22dd2635ab876f57bc22ee758a7f55d776","tid":1895134,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}